{"title_page": "List of Fenerbah\u00e7e S.K. records and statistics", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n[[File:IlkSampiyonlar.jpg|thumb|300px|right|Fenerbah\u00e7e squad that won the [[1911\u201312 Istanbul Football League]]]]\n'''List of Fenerbah\u00e7e S.K. records and statistics''' contains the records and statistics of the footballers of [[Fenerbah\u00e7e S.K. (football)|Fenerbah\u00e7e]].\n\nDomestically, Fenerbah\u00e7e has 19 [[S\u00fcper Lig]], 6 [[Turkish Cup]] and 9 [[Turkish Super Cup]] titles.<ref name=\"m\u00fcze\">{{cite news | title = M\u00fczemiz | url = http://www.fenerbahce.org/kurumsal/detay.asp?ContentID=23 | work = fenerbahce.org | publisher = Fenerbah\u00e7e Spor Kul\u00fcb\u00fc | access-date = 4 August 2013 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150407000516/http://www.fenerbahce.org/kurumsal/detay.asp?ContentID=23 | archive-date = 7 April 2015}}</ref> In european cups, the club has 1 [[Balkans Cup]] title, and this cup is the first european cup that comes to [[Turkey]].<ref name=\"uluslararas\u0131\">{{cite news | title = Uluslararas\u0131 Ba\u015far\u0131lar\u0131m\u0131z | url = http://www.fenerbahce.org.tr/detay.asp?ContentID=23311 | work = fenerbahce.org | publisher = Fenerbah\u00e7e Spor Kul\u00fcb\u00fc | access-date = 4 August 2013}}</ref>\n\n==Honours==\n===European competitions===\n* '''[[Balkans Cup]]'''\n: '''Winners (1):''' [[1966\u201367 Balkans Cup|1966\u201367]]\n\n===Domestic competitions===\n'''National Championships'''\n* '''[[S\u00fcper Lig|Turkish Super League]]'''\n: '''Winners (19):''' [[1959 Milli Lig|1959]], [[1960\u201361 Milli Lig|1960\u201361]], [[1963\u201364 1.Lig|1963\u201364]], [[1964\u201365 1.Lig|1964\u201365]], [[1967\u201368 1.Lig|1967\u201368]], [[1969\u201370 1.Lig|1969\u201370]], [[1973\u201374 1.Lig|1973\u201374]], [[1974\u201375 1.Lig|1974\u201375]], [[1977\u201378 1.Lig|1977\u201378]], [[1982\u201383 1.Lig|1982\u201383]], [[1984\u201385 1.Lig|1984\u201385]], [[1988\u201389 1.Lig|1988\u201389]], [[1995\u201396 1.Lig|1995\u201396]], [[2000\u201301 1.Lig|2000\u201301]], [[2003\u201304 S\u00fcper Lig|2003\u201304]], [[2004\u201305 S\u00fcper Lig|2004\u201305]], [[2006\u201307 S\u00fcper Lig|2006\u201307]], [[2010\u201311 S\u00fcper Lig|2010\u201311]], [[2013\u201314 S\u00fcper Lig|2013\u201314]]\n: ''Runners-up (22):'' [[1959-60 Milli Lig|1959\u201360]], [[1961-62 Milli Lig|1961\u201362]], [[1966-67 1.Lig|1966\u201367]], [[1970-71 1.Lig|1970\u201371]], [[1972-73 1.Lig|1972\u201373]], [[1975\u201376 1.Lig|1975\u201376]], [[1976\u201377 1.Lig|1976\u201377]], [[1979\u201380 1.Lig|1979\u201380]], [[1983\u201384 1.Lig|1983\u201384]], [[1989-90 1.Lig|1989\u201390]], [[1991-92 1.Lig|1991\u201392]], [[1993-94 1.Lig|1993\u201394]], [[1997-98 1.Lig|1997\u201398]], [[2001-02 S\u00fcper Lig|2001\u201302]], [[2005-06 S\u00fcper Lig|2005\u201306]], [[2007-08 S\u00fcper Lig|2007\u201308]], [[2009\u201310 S\u00fcper Lig|2009\u201310]], [[2011\u201312 S\u00fcper Lig|2011\u201312]], [[2012\u201313 S\u00fcper Lig|2012\u201313]], [[2014\u201315 S\u00fcper Lig|2014\u201315]], [[2015\u201316 S\u00fcper Lig|2015\u201316]], [[2017\u201318 S\u00fcper Lig|2017\u201318]]\n\n* '''[[Turkish National Division]]'''\n: '''Winners (6) (record):''' [[1937 Turkish National Division|1937]], [[1940 Turkish National Division|1940]], [[1943 Turkish National Division|1943]], [[1945 Turkish National Division|1945]], [[1946 Turkish National Division|1946]], [[1950 Turkish National Division|1950]]\n: ''Runners-up (2):'' [[1944 Turkish National Division|1944]], [[1947 Turkish National Division|1947]]\n\n* '''[[Turkish Football Championship]]\n: '''Winners (3) (shared-record):''' [[1933 Turkish Football Championship|1933]], [[1935 Turkish Football Championship|1935]], [[1944 Turkish Football Championship|1944]]\n: ''Runners-up (2):'' [[1940 Turkish Football Championship|1940]], [[1947 Turkish Football Championship|1947]]\n\n'''National Cups'''\n* '''[[Turkish Cup]]'''\n: '''Winners (6):''' [[Turkish Cup#Winners|1967\u201368]], [[Turkish Cup#Winners|1973\u201374]], [[Turkish Cup#Winners|1978\u201379]], [[Turkish Cup#Winners|1982\u201383]], [[2012 Turkish Cup Final|2011\u201312]], [[Turkish Cup#Winners|2012\u201313]]\n: ''Runners-up (11):'' [[Turkish Cup#Winners|1962\u201363]], [[Turkish Cup#Winners|1964\u201365]], [[Turkish Cup#Winners|1988\u201389]], [[Turkish Cup#Winners|1995\u201396]], [[Turkish Cup#Winners|2000\u201301]], [[2005 Turkish Cup Final|2004\u201305]], [[2006 Turkish Cup Final|2005\u201306]], [[2009 Turkish Cup Final|2008\u201309]], [[2010 Turkish Cup Final|2009\u201310]], [[2015\u201316 Turkish Cup#Final|2015\u201316]], [[2017\u201318 Turkish Cup#Final|2017\u201318]]\n\n* '''[[Turkish Super Cup]]'''\n: '''Winners (9):''' [[1968 Presidential Cup|1968]], [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1973]], [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1975]], [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1984]], [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1985]], [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1990]], [[2007 Turkish Super Cup|2007]], [[2009 Turkish Super Cup|2009]], [[2014 Turkish Super Cup|2014]]\n: ''Runners-up (9):'' [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1970]], [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1974]], [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1978]], [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1979]], [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1983]], [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1989]], [[Turkish Super Cup#Finals|1996]], [[2012 Turkish Super Cup|2012]], [[2013 Turkish Super Cup|2013]]\n\n* '''[[Atat\u00fcrk Cup]]''' \n: '''Winners (2) (record):''' 1964, [[1998 Atat\u00fcrk Cup|1998]]\n\n* '''[[Prime Minister's Cup]]''' \n: '''Winners (8) (record):''' 1945, 1946, 1950, 1973, 1980, 1989, 1993, 1998\n: ''Runners-up (7):'' 1944, 1971, 1976, 1977, 1992, 1994, 1995\n\n===Regional competitions===\n* '''[[Istanbul Football League]]''' \n: '''Winners (16) (record):''' [[1911\u201312 Istanbul Football League|1911\u201312]], [[1913\u201314 Istanbul Football League|1913\u201314]], [[1914\u201315 Istanbul Football League|1914\u201315]], [[1920\u201321 Istanbul Football League|